The new R'Space faculty and staff portals are a revolution in information dissemination. These fully customizable pages place all your commonly used tools and resources at your fingertips. From Webmail to traffic and weather reports, to specialized web based applications, you select and access the content you want to see. At the same time, the portals will allow the University to let you know what is going on around our campus.Your first time in the new portal? The UCR portal is a powerful tool, but like any tool, it is important to take a moment to learn how to use it correctly. If you are new to portals, we invite you to review our tutorial. Also, we encourage you to bookmark this page in your Web browser, as we think you will be coming here often.